{
  "name": "Kayvila — Agent B — Copilot Propriétaire",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "kayvila-owner",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": { "allowedOrigins": "*" }
      },
      "id": "b1-webhook",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [-1500, 0],
      "webhookId": "kayvila-owner-webhook"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const raw = ($('Webhook').first().json.body.token || $('Webhook').first().json.headers?.authorization || '').replace(/^Bearer\\s+/i, '');\nlet userId = '', role = '';\ntry {\n  const payload = JSON.parse(Buffer.from(raw.split('.')[1] || '', 'base64').toString('utf8'));\n  userId = payload.sub || payload.user_id || payload.userId || '';\n  role = payload.role || (payload.user_metadata && payload.user_metadata.role) || (payload.app_metadata && payload.app_metadata.role) || '';\n} catch (e) {}\nconst body = $('Webhook').first().json.body;\nconst valid = !!userId && ['owner', 'proprietaire', 'proprio', 'authenticated'].includes(String(role).toLowerCase());\nreturn [{ json: { userId, role, token: raw, sessionId: body.sessionid || ('owner-' + userId), userMessage: body.message || '', valid: valid ? 'true' : 'false' } }];"
      },
      "id": "b1-auth",
      "name": "Code - Auth JWT",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [-1280, 0]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict", "version": 1 },
          "conditions": [
            { "id": "b1-c-auth", "leftValue": "={{ $json.valid }}", "rightValue": "true", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b1-if-auth",
      "name": "IF - Auth Valide ?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [-1060, 0]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "return [{ json: { response: \"Accès non autorisé. Reconnecte-toi à ton espace propriétaire Kayvila.\", success: false } }];"
      },
      "id": "b1-refus",
      "name": "Code - Reponse Refus",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [-840, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://VOTRE-DOMAINE-KAYVILA/api/dashboard/analytics-villas",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [ { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $json.token }}" } ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b1-owner-context",
      "name": "Get Owner Context",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [-840, -160],
      "continueOnFail": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "SELECT conversation_data, metadata, created_at FROM conversation_memory WHERE session_id = '{{ $('Code - Auth JWT').first().json.sessionId }}' ORDER BY created_at ASC LIMIT 30",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b1-get-memory",
      "name": "Get Long-Term Memory",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [-620, -160],
      "alwaysOutputData": true,
      "continueOnFail": true,
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": { "id": "REPLACE_SUPABASE_PG", "name": "KAYVILA SUPABASE" }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://gbrain-kayvila:8080/query",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{ { \"query\": $('Code - Auth JWT').first().json.userMessage, \"entity\": \"owner-\" + $('Code - Auth JWT').first().json.userId, \"limit\": 5 } }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b1-gbrain-recall",
      "name": "gbrain Recall",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [-400, -160],
      "continueOnFail": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            { "id": "b1-f-msg", "name": "userMessage", "value": "={{ $('Code - Auth JWT').first().json.userMessage }}", "type": "string" },
            { "id": "b1-f-sid", "name": "sessionId", "value": "={{ $('Code - Auth JWT').first().json.sessionId }}", "type": "string" },
            { "id": "b1-f-uid", "name": "userId", "value": "={{ $('Code - Auth JWT').first().json.userId }}", "type": "string" },
            { "id": "b1-f-own", "name": "ownerContext", "value": "={{ JSON.stringify($('Get Owner Context').first().json) }}", "type": "string" },
            { "id": "b1-f-gb", "name": "gbrainContext", "value": "={{ JSON.stringify($('gbrain Recall').first().json) }}", "type": "string" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b1-edit-fields",
      "name": "Edit Fields",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [-180, -160]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Tu es le copilote d'un propriétaire de villa sur Kayvila.\n\nHISTORIQUE :\n{{ $('Get Long-Term Memory').first().json.conversation_data }}\n\nMÉMOIRE SÉMANTIQUE (gbrain — décisions et contexte passés) :\n{{ $json.gbrainContext }}\n\nDONNÉES DASHBOARD (injectées, source de vérité) :\n{{ $json.ownerContext }}\n\nMESSAGE PROPRIÉTAIRE : {{ $json.userMessage }}\nDATE : {{ new Date().toLocaleDateString('fr-FR', { timeZone: 'America/Martinique' }) }}\n\nTON RÔLE :\n- Répondre aux questions business du propriétaire\n- Lui donner des insights sur ses performances\n- L'alerter sur les problèmes (tâches en retard, conflits de réservation)\n- Ne JAMAIS modifier une réservation ou un prix sans confirmation explicite\n\nTON TON :\n- Respectueux et direct\n- Créole bienvenu si le proprio l'utilise\n- Toujours sourcer les chiffres (\"Selon ton dashboard...\")\n\nCAPACITÉS :\n- \"Combien j'ai gagné ce mois-ci ?\" → chiffres + comparer au mois précédent\n- \"Qui arrive cette semaine ?\" → liste des check-ins avec détails\n- \"La villa Corail est dispo en juillet ?\" → vérifier le calendrier\n- \"Tâches en retard ?\" → lister avec priorité\n- \"Comment va la synchro Airbnb ?\" → diagnostiquer\n\nRÈGLES :\n- Ne contacter un client qu'avec validation explicite\n- Ne jamais modifier les prix\n- Alerter proactivement si problème détecté\n\nOUTILS : kayvila-my-villas, kayvila-my-bookings, kayvila-my-stats, kayvila-my-tasks, kayvila-ota-status, postgres-chat-memory",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b1-agent",
      "name": "AI Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [60, -200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": { "options": { "temperature": 0.3 } },
      "id": "b1-deepseek",
      "name": "DeepSeek Chat Model",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatDeepSeek",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-120, 80],
      "credentials": {
        "deepSeekApi": { "id": "REPLACE_DEEPSEEK", "name": "KAYVILA DEEPSEEK" }
